  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a move action, you can alter the amount of light shed by any nonmagical light source within 60 feet so that its light radius is either halved or doubled.</p>\n<p>At 1st level, you can affect light sources up to the size of a torch.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, you can affect any Medium or smaller nonmagical light source (such as a campfire).</p>\n<p>At 14th level, you can affect Large or smaller nonmagical light sources (such as bonfires) and magical light sources up to the size of an everburning torch. If a creature is holding the light source you are trying to affect, the creature can attempt a Reflex save to avoid the effect.</p>",
